# Force Vercel's Python builder to install the slim root requirements.txt rather
# than the full project. Vercel installs from uv.lock (or pyproject.toml) when
# present — the whole locked stack (jupyter, pyarrow, scipy, scikit-learn,
# matplotlib, tconnectsync) is ~654 MB, over the 500 MB limit. Hiding both makes
# it fall back to requirements.txt (~130 MB).
uv.lock
pyproject.toml

# Not needed in the worker at runtime; keeps the upload small.
.venv
data
test_data
research.ipynb
apps/web
apps/local
*.parquet
*.csv
